Super Global High School

00:13:33.730 --> 00:13:35.815 position:50% align:center
has Kuonji,
and he's no joke.

00:13:35.899 --> 00:13:38.276 position:50% align:center
From what I've heard,
he's Shinozaki's old rival.

00:13:38.360 --> 00:13:40.403 position:50% align:center
I'm the one who's
gonna beat Shinozaki.

00:13:40.487 --> 00:13:43.531 position:50% align:center
Yeah, yeah. We know already.
Stay, stay.

00:13:43.615 --> 00:13:46.451 position:50% align:center
