00:13:46.534 --> 00:13:47.911 position:50% align:center
Keep your calm, man.

00:13:47.994 --> 00:13:51.706 position:50% align:center
Uh, like, it means you're
cooler when you remain calm.

00:13:51.790 --> 00:13:52.874 position:50% align:center
[MAESHIMA]
Huh...

00:13:52.957 --> 00:13:54.334 position:50% align:center
Going back to what
we were saying,

00:13:54.417 --> 00:13:56.419 position:50% align:center
Kuonji's teammates'
skill levels are actually

00:13:56.503 --> 00:13:58.922 position:50% align:center
a total mystery.
They seem like entertai--

00:13:59.005 --> 00:14:00.465 position:50% align:center
[YUKIMITSU]
You don't believe in Rui's team?

