00:14:03.301 --> 00:14:05.428 position:50% align:center
[YUKIMITSU] Do you even get
how hard they've worked? Hm?

00:14:05.512 --> 00:14:06.721 position:50% align:center
Right, um, I'm sorry--

00:14:06.805 --> 00:14:08.598 position:50% align:center
[YUKIMITSU]
I'm not digging for an apology!

00:14:08.682 --> 00:14:10.767 position:50% align:center
The thing is, being unknown
doesn't necessarily

00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:11.935 position:50% align:center
mean they're unskilled.

00:14:12.018 --> 00:14:13.478 position:50% align:center
Yes! That! Thank you!

