Skaters, please leave the ice.
Repeat...

00:14:24.906 --> 00:14:26.366 position:50% align:center
Guys, you've done
great sticking with me

00:14:26.449 --> 00:14:27.617 position:50% align:center
up until now.

00:14:27.701 --> 00:14:29.536 position:50% align:center
And here we are with
our final performance

00:14:29.619 --> 00:14:31.788 position:50% align:center
