to be proud of.

00:14:44.551 --> 00:14:48.179 position:50% align:center
I, for one, take pride
in this team.

00:14:48.263 --> 00:14:49.931 position:50% align:center
Now that we're here,
I say we give the best

00:14:50.015 --> 00:14:52.809 position:50% align:center
