and grab all the glory!

00:14:52.892 --> 00:14:54.144 position:50% align:center
Us five, together!

00:14:54.227 --> 00:14:55.562 position:50% align:center
[SUZAKI]
Yes!

00:14:55.645 --> 00:14:57.022 position:50% align:center
[MIKADO] We're gonna skate
in the Grand Prix finals!

00:14:57.105 --> 00:14:58.023 position:50% align:center
