And we'll win it!

00:14:58.106 --> 00:14:59.399 position:50% align:center
Let's do this, Captain!

00:15:01.276 --> 00:15:02.235 position:50% align:center
[KUONJI]
Here we go.

00:15:02.318 --> 00:15:03.403 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:15:03.486 --> 00:15:05.822 position:50% align:center
We're Yokohama Super
Global High School!

