with no regrets.

00:16:00.085 --> 00:16:01.044 position:50% align:center
Yeah!

00:16:01.127 --> 00:16:03.338 position:50% align:center
It's fine, you know,
having regrets.

00:16:04.297 --> 00:16:07.258 position:50% align:center
[HIMEKAWA] Today will not
